            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價上漲打壓降息預期 美元指數邁向2024年以來最佳單周表現",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3c2Z1sJa.pVvtFi8erU6VQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/13d2efbd4d5a719fae8b7b913548a2fe\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> （本文為機器翻譯，準確性基於第三方軟件服務，反饋請點擊）</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在中東衝突升級和油價飆升之際，美元作為避險資產走強，本周勢將錄得逾一年來最佳表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博美元即期指數本周以來上漲1.4%，為2024年底以來最大單周漲幅。自上周末美國與以色列對伊朗發動打擊以來，布倫特原油期貨價格累計上漲約25%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">敵對行動擾亂了原油生產和航運，並加劇對聯儲會及其他央行面臨通膨壓力的擔憂。這促使交易員削減對聯儲會降息的押注，從而進一步提振美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c6a3d023-8c01-33b3-8366-4778bc296e9f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五公佈的報告顯示美國非農就業人數意外驟減，這為經濟前景增添複雜性。不過，由於市場焦點主要集中在能源價格，該數據僅短暫壓制美元走勢，美元很快重拾升勢。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tkBrfxUkzjAq5j5yCAFOLw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8411d2cc30a2cc2f29c0afae3a9ad6d1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Dollar Heads for Best Week Since 2024 as Oil Surge Trims Fed Bet</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E9%82%81%E5%90%912024%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E5%96%AE%E5%91%A8%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-160256715.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 00:48:26",
