        {
            "title": "中國稱「歐盟製造」計畫大搞保護主義 構成嚴重投資壁壘和制度性歧視",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國批評歐盟最新發布的一項要求成員國在公共採購中優先選擇本土企業的計畫，稱此舉構成嚴重投資壁壘和制度性歧視。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據中國商務部網站刊發的聲明，對歐盟周三發布的《工業加速器法案》表示「嚴重關切」，該法案對於外國企業投資電池、電動汽車、光伏、關鍵原物料四大行業設置了強制技術轉讓、外資股比、產品本地含量及本地員工等限制條款，進一步加大了中國企業投資歐盟的不確定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國商務部表示，歐盟以發展相關產業和推動綠色轉型為由，築牆設壘，大搞保護主義，將破壞公平競爭，擾亂全球產供鏈穩定。商務部發言人呼籲歐方帶頭遵守世貿規則，盡快回到公平透明和非歧視的合作軌道上來。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a2f520b1-a5b6-3578-8ed6-d6b2494028f8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「中方將密切關注相關立法進程，認真評估對中方利益的影響，並將堅決維護中國企業合法正當權益，」該發言人稱。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟的《工業加速器法案》旨在確保到2035年製造業占歐盟經濟產出的五分之一。這項被稱為「歐盟製造」的提案，重點覆蓋鋼鐵、水泥等高排放行業，以及電池、核能等清潔技術和汽車產業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該計畫是歐盟加碼支持汽車和綠色鋼鐵等戰略產業、遏制工廠關閉潮的關鍵抓手。相關提案仍需成員國和歐洲議會批准，可能耗時一至兩年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Criticizes EU’s ‘Made in Europe’ Plan as Protectionist</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A8%B1-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0-%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E5%A4%A7%E6%90%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9-%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%A3%81%E5%A3%98%E5%92%8C%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E6%80%A7%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-160230918.html",
